@node "PGP signatures" "PGP signatures"

   CHECKING PGP SIGNATURES:
   ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
     Make sure you've got my @{" Public Key " link "Public Key" 0}.
     If you don't trust the one in this file, request it via @{" E-Mail " link "JHL" 0}.

   1. MAIL:

     Save the mailmessage as a file called : VList
     Type in CLI : pgp Vlist Vlist.guide

   2. ARCHIVE:

     Type in CLI : pgp VirusScanList.guide.sig VirusScanList.guide

     Do this for VList-History.TXT, FILE_ID.DIZ & VHT-VLIST.diz also.
@endnode

