@node "Abbreviations" "Abbreviations"

   ABBREVIATIONS:
   ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
   UP = Unpacked    TR = Trojan         INS = Installer
   PP = Packed      FV = File Virus     INF = Infiltrator
   FK = Fake        LV = Link Virus     STB = Supposed to be
   BV = BootVirus   /X = Ami Express    IBA = Including BBS adds
   DV = DiskValid.

   @{" Back to the List " link "VirusScanList" 0}
@endnode

